Architecture: i386 amd64 ppc64 powerpc ia64 s390 arm armel armhf sh4 mips mipsel
XC-Package-Type: udeb
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: tools to support fast kexec reboots (udeb)
